high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up the fork from the sink.
Move to the right and look up at the upper right cabinet.
Put the fork in the cup in the cabinet.
Pick up the cup with the fork in it.
Turn around and go to the white table on your left.
Put the cup with the fork on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a fork inside a cup on the white table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up a fork in the sink.
Turn right and go to the cupboard above the counter.
Put the fork in the cup in the cupboard.
Pick up the cup from the cupboard.
Turn around and go to the table.
Put the cup on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move the cup from the cupboard to the table.

high_descs: Move to the sink to the right of the microwave.
Pick up a fork from the sink.
Move to the end of the counter to the right of the sink.
Open the top right hand cabinet and place the fork in a cup.
Pick up the cup with the fork and close the cabinet.
Move to the table behind you.
Place the cup on the table to the left of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork on the table to the left of the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and hang a left at the stove to reach the sink.
Pick up the fork from the middle of the sink.
Head right to the wall and turn left to face the counter.
Place the fork inside the gold cup in the far right upper cabinet.
Pick up the gold cup with the fork inside of it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the white table on your left.
Place the gold cup with the fork inside to the left of the head of lettuce on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink at the other side of the room.
Pick up the fork that is in the sink.
Go to the cabinets to the right of the sink.
Open the far right cabinet above the counter and put the fork inside the wine glass.
Remove the wine glass from the cupboard.
Turn around and go to the white table on the left side of the room with the lettuce on it.
Set the wine glass on the table to the left of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a wine glass with a fork inside of it on a table.
